  - atc_4: The chemical and functional group of  is tetracyclines.
  - category: Omadacycline is part of Anti-Bacterial Agents ; Antibacterials for Systemic Use ; Antiinfectives for Systemic Use ; Naphthacenes ; P-glycoprotein substrates ; Tetracyclines.
  - group: Omadacycline is approved and investigational.

